// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0721 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: e629fd9f-d253-527e-be24-fcb423eda44e

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*azure linux:3.0*" or process.executable like~ "*chainguard:*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:20.04-ESM*")
